<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-88-0301 </DOCNO><TEXT>This report presents the results of an evaluation of the present ToxicWaste Control Operations at the Lawrence Livermore National Laboratory,evaluates the technologies most applicable to the treatment of toxicand hazardous wastes and presents conceptual designs of processes forthe installation of a new decontamination and waste treatment facility(DWTF) for future treatment of these wastes.</TEXT></DOC>